== 製作 ==
=== 開發 ===
2019年11月，在第二季完結之前，DC漫畫宣佈預訂第三季<ref name="Season 3">{{cite web |last1=Freeman |first1=Molly |title=DC's ''Titans'' Season 3 Officially Happening, Will Release 2020 |url=https://screenrant.com/dc-titans-season-3-renewal-2020-release-date/ |website=Screen Rant |date=2019-11-11 |accessdate=2019-11-11 |language=en-US |archive-date=2019-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111193931/https://screenrant.com/dc-titans-season-3-renewal-2020-release-date/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last1=Griffin |first1=David |title=DC Universe's ''Titans'' Season 3 Renewal Announcement |url=https://www.ign.com/articles/2019/11/11/dc-universes-titans-season-3-renewal-announcement |website=IGN |date=2019-11-11 |accessdate=2019-11-11 |language=en-US |archive-date=2019-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111193933/https://www.ign.com/articles/2019/11/11/dc-universes-titans-season-3-renewal-announcement |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2020年3月，受[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]影響，製作組被迫延遲拍攝工作<ref name="Pandemic">{{cite web |last1=Mancuso |first1=Vinnie |title=‘Titans’ Season 3: Akiva Goldsman Offers Update on Filming |url=https://collider.com/titans-season-3-update-akiva-goldsman/ |website=[[Collider_(website)|Collider]] |accessdate=2020-07-07 |date=2020-05-17 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115212740/https://collider.com/titans-season-3-update-akiva-goldsman/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2020年8月，[[華納媒體|華納媒體]]宣佈包括《泰坦》在內的多部[[DC_Universe_(串流媒體)|DC Universe]]的原創劇集移至[[HBO_Max|HBO Max]]播出<ref name="HBOMax">{{cite web |last1=Mitovich |first1=Matt Webb |title=DC Universe Original TV Series Will Be Moving to HBO Max, Says DC CCO |url=https://tvline.com/2020/08/14/dc-universe-original-series-moving-hbo-max-titans/ |website=TV Line |accessdate=2020-08-23 |date=2020-08-14 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115212618/https://tvline.com/2020/08/14/dc-universe-original-series-moving-hbo-max-titans/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第三季為本劇在HBO Max播出的首季<ref name="DCInfinite">{{cite web |last1=Agard |first1=Chancellor |title=DC Universe to become premium comics service as TV originals move to HBO Max |url=https://ew.com/tv/dc-universe-infinite-titans-hbo-max/ |website=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]] |accessdate=2020-09-18 |date=2020-09-18 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-09-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919062215/https://ew.com/tv/dc-universe-infinite-titans-hbo-max/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 劇本 ===
2020年8月，節目統籌葛瑞格·沃克表示第三季將發生在[[高譚市|高譚市]]，並引入[[紅頭罩|紅頭罩]]、[[稻草人_(漫畫)|「稻草人」強納森·克萊恩]]和[[芭芭拉·高登|芭芭拉·高登]]<ref name="Season3Character">{{cite web |last1=Lawrence |first1=Gregory |title=‘Titans’ Season 3 Is Adding Barbara Gordon, Scarecrow, and Red Hood |url=https://collider.com/titans-season-3-new-characters-red-hood/ |website=[[Collider_(website)|Collider]] |accessdate=2020-08-22 |date=2020-08-22 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115212612/https://collider.com/titans-season-3-new-characters-red-hood/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="RedHood">{{cite web |last1=Mitovich |first1=Matt Webb |title=Titans Season 3 Will Head to Gotham, Add Barbara Gordon and Red Hood |url=https://tvline.com/2020/08/22/titans-season-3-casting-barbara-gordon-scarecrow/ |website=TV Line |accessdate=2020-08-22 |date=2020-08-22 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115212622/https://tvline.com/2020/08/22/titans-season-3-casting-barbara-gordon-scarecrow/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。稍後消息透露，本季的背景原初仍設定為[[舊金山|舊金山]]，由於拍攝延期至秋冬季節，故事背景轉至高譚市<ref name="Season3NewDetails">{{cite web |last1=Kaya |first1=Emre |title=Exclusive: New Details About ‘Titans’ Season 3 |url=https://www.thevulcanreporter.com/exclusives/titans-season-3-details-scarecrow-red-hood/ |website=The Vulcan Reporter |accessdate=2020-09-04 |date=2020-09-04 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916192050/https://www.thevulcanreporter.com/exclusives/titans-season-3-details-scarecrow-red-hood/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。9月，沃克表示[[唐娜·特洛伊|唐娜·-{特洛伊}-／神力女孩]]儘管在第二季中死去，仍將回歸第三季<ref name="Return">{{cite web |last1=Flook |first1=Ray |title=Titans Season 3: Conor Leslie Set to Return as Donna Troy |url=https://bleedingcool.com/tv/titans-season-3-conor-leslie-set-to-return-as-donna-troy/ |website=Bleeding Cool |accessdate=2020-09-15 |date=2020-09-12 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916234008/https://bleedingcool.com/tv/titans-season-3-conor-leslie-set-to-return-as-donna-troy/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Teaser">{{cite web |last1=Galanis |first1=Evangelia |title=Titans EP Teases a Return for Donna Troy |url=https://www.cbr.com/titans-ep-teases-donna-troy-return/amp/?fbclid=IwAR3sMb8S5WN4NZznWeRg62zpA5WNz5QYjZE2hkFS4K0wpTTaTSvNUmGDUho |website=Comic Book Resources |accessdate=2020-09-15 |date=2020-09-12 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200916224333/https://www.cbr.com/titans-ep-teases-donna-troy-return/amp/?fbclid=IwAR3sMb8S5WN4NZznWeRg62zpA5WNz5QYjZE2hkFS4K0wpTTaTSvNUmGDUho |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 選角 ===
[[布蘭頓·思懷茲|布蘭頓·思懷茲]]、{{le|安娜·迪奧普|Anna Diop}}、[[蒂根·卡芙特|蒂根·卡芙特]]、[[瑞恩·波特|瑞恩·波特]]、{{le|克蘭·華特斯|Curran Walters}}、{{le|康娜·萊斯里|Conor Leslie}}、{{le|雀兒喜·張|Chelsea Zhang}}、約書亞·奧平（{{lang|en|Joshua Orpin}}）、[[敏卡·凱利|敏卡·凱利]]和[[阿倫·瑞奇森|阿倫·瑞奇森]]回歸主演，第二季客串演員{{le|達瑪莉絲·路易斯|Damaris Lewis}}被提升為主演<ref name="LewisS3">{{Cite web|url=https://tvline.com/2019/12/02/titans-season-3-damaris-lewis-series-regular-blackfire/|title=''Titans'' Season 3: Damaris Lewis Promoted to Series Regular as Blackfire|first1=Matt Webb|last1=Mitovich|website=TVLine|date=2019-12-02|accessdate=2019-12-04|language=en-US|archive-date=2020-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201115212625/https://tvline.com/2019/12/02/titans-season-3-damaris-lewis-series-regular-blackfire/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2020年4月，[[伊恩·格雷|伊恩·格雷]]確定回歸客串出演[[布魯斯·韋恩|布魯斯·韋恩]]<ref name="Bruce">{{cite web |last1=Perine |first1=Aaron |title=Titans: Iain Glen's Bruce Wayne Will Return in Season 3 |url=https://comicbook.com/dc/news/titans-bruce-wayne-iain-glen-will-return-season-three/ |website=Comicbook.com |access-date=2020-10-19 |date=2020-04-04 |language=en-US |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130115702/https://comicbook.com/dc/news/titans-bruce-wayne-iain-glen-will-return-season-three/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2021年1月，{{le|莎凡娜·魏爾奇|Savannah Welch}}確定出演[[芭芭拉·高登|芭芭拉·高登]]<ref name ="Barbara">{{Cite web|last=Otterson|first=Joe|last2=Otterson|first2=Joe|date=2021-01-19|title=‘Titans’ Season 3 Casts Savannah Welch as Barbara Gordon (EXCLUSIVE)|url=https://variety.com/2021/tv/news/titans-season-3-barbara-gordon-savannah-welch-1234886752/|access-date=2021-01-19|website=Variety|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119191302/https://variety.com/2021/tv/news/titans-season-3-barbara-gordon-savannah-welch-1234886752/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。4月，[[文森特·卡塞瑟|文森特·卡塞瑟]]確定出演[[稻草人_(漫畫)|「稻草人」強納森·克萊恩]]<ref name="VincentK">{{Cite web|date=2021-04-28|title='Mad Men' Alum Vincent Kartheiser to Play Scarecrow on HBO Max's 'Titans'|url=https://www.thewrap.com/titans-scarecrow-vincent-kartheiser/|first=Tim|last=Baysinger|access-date=2021-04-28|website=TheWrap|language=en-US|archive-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430123131/https://www.thewrap.com/titans-scarecrow-vincent-kartheiser/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

